Executive Summary

The wordcloud is used to find out the main reasons for businesses who received positive and negative feedback?“ so that businesses can use the information for strategy planning.

Results for Positive sentiments

From the wordcloud diagram, most of the customers feel that it is great food, great place and great price.

Results for Negative sentiments

From the wordcloud diagram, most of the customers feel that it is waste time, horrible service and waste money.

Summary

The above model of using wordcloud proved to be reliable to provide the main reasons for businesses who received positive and negative feedback so that the businesses can use it for their strategy planning.
